      "text": "\ud83c\udfaf  My Trader Assistant\n\n[ Orchestrator ]\n\nSystem Prompt:\n\u2022 Client coverage goals\n\u2022 Risk parameters\n\u2022 Sector focus\n\u2022 Alert sensitivity\n\u2022 Trade idea themes\n\nReceives signals \u2192\nSpawns subagents \u2192\nMerges responses",
